Technology has progressed to the point in which the justice system is entirely 
managed by an all-knowing artificial intelligence. In the early 21 century, a 
computer called MIL14-RD was built to become the ultimate arbiter of human transgression.

This worked, until people started going missing.

You, a retired investigator, have decided to interrogate MIL14-RD by hacking into it's 
mainframe. You have no leads, except the name "Thomas Jones", a man who existed yesterday...

When you are ready, type "enter" to contact MIL14-RD